<C>__{anna}
<D>__{it's getting cold.}
<A>__{malcolm crowe sits on the floor at the coffee table, his vest and tie on the sofa behind him. a jacket and an overcoat lay on a brirfcase next to him. malcolm is in his thirties with thick, wavy hair and striking, intelligent eyes that squint from years of intense study. his charming, easy going smile spreads across his face. he points.}
<C>__{malcolm}
<D>__{that's one fine frame. a fine frame it is.}
